short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: YouTube Ads Checklist with a step by step guide to building out your own targeted audiences with Google ads remarketing

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
YouTube Ads Checklist. How To Set Up a YouTube Ads Campaign Step-By-Step.

This checklist takes you by the hand with screenshots and steps to set up YouTube 'In-Feed' Ads Or Alternatively Instream Ads campaigns WITHOUT a conversion goal.

I personally use this strategy to build out laser targeted audiences by adding viewers of my video ads to remarketing audiences that build within my Google ads account.

These audiences are then use to build larger audiences going forward and are available for me use for promotions within my niche any time.

Try it out, its free and if you want to start learning how to drive traffic from YouTube with very low cost per view, all the details you need to get started is covered in this chrome extension checklist.
